1
00:00:10,940 --> 00:00:14,020
ظآزLove crosses every cycle
of life and deathظآز

2
00:00:14,300 --> 00:00:17,580
ظآزSo let me fall with youظآز

3
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,420
ظآزAll the noise of the mortal worldظآز

4
00:00:20,420 --> 00:00:24,060
ظآزIs nothing compared to her eyesظآز

5
00:00:24,060 --> 00:00:27,180
ظآزWhoever said love itself is sinظآز

6
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,020
ظآزWhen a heartbeat turns into
wind and moonlightظآز

7
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,180
ظآزPainting a banquet
of endless spring bloomsظآز

8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 27=

11
00:01:04,700 --> 00:01:07,700
ظآزLies born in the mire of schemesظآز

12
00:01:07,700 --> 00:01:09,900
ظآزHave trapped our fateظآز

13
00:01:11,580 --> 00:01:14,420
ظآزA dead knot, pulled by love and hateظآز

14
00:01:14,540 --> 00:01:16,980
ظآزShattered by your bladeظآز

15
00:01:17,540 --> 00:01:18,700
ظآزPear blossoms in the courtyardظآز

16
00:01:19,719 --> 00:01:20,519
Mei Lin,

17
00:01:21,519 --> 00:01:22,799
dawn is breaking.

18
00:01:22,799 --> 00:01:24,660
ظآزOnly burn more fiercelyظآز

19
00:01:24,940 --> 00:01:27,700
ظآزIf all our past were lostظآز

20
00:01:27,860 --> 00:01:31,220
ظآزOnly leaving longing behindظآز

21
00:01:32,180 --> 00:01:35,020
ظآزUse the lovebound poison
to tie us togetherظآز

22
00:01:35,060 --> 00:01:37,860
ظآزEven in pain, let me get closer to youظآز

23
00:01:38,140 --> 00:01:39,500
ظآزMay this illusionظآز

24
00:01:39,580 --> 00:01:44,540
ظآزOf sweetness last a little longerظآز

25
00:01:44,940 --> 00:01:46,580
ظآزJust let youظآز

26
00:01:46,740 --> 00:01:49,260
ظآزThrow this dream into the flamesظآز

27
00:01:49,260 --> 00:01:51,540
ظآزAnd let it endظآز

28
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:23,560
(Mei Lin,)

29
00:02:25,479 --> 00:02:27,120
(I'll set you free.)

30
00:02:55,620 --> 00:02:58,300
(Tablet of Empress Mei Lin)

31
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:24,120
You drove my birth mother to her death,

32
00:03:26,479 --> 00:03:28,199
and now you've driven

33
00:03:28,599 --> 00:03:29,879
my empress to hers as well.

34
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,360
Now,

35
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,919
are you satisfied?

36
00:03:43,060 --> 00:03:44,560
(Tablet of Empress Mei Lin)

37
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:45,439
(Tablet of Empress Mei Lin)
Issue the decree!

38
00:03:46,599 --> 00:03:47,960
From this day forward,

39
00:03:48,319 --> 00:03:49,919
Daliang shall never again
have an empress.

40
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:52,479
Whoever mentions it will have

41
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,400
their clan erased!

42
00:03:56,759 --> 00:03:57,560
(History records)

43
00:03:57,759 --> 00:03:59,680
(that Murong Jinghe,
Emperor of Daliang,)

44
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:01,000
(reigned for forty years.)

45
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,759
(His harem stood empty,)

46
00:04:02,919 --> 00:04:04,439
(and he never named an empress again.)

47
00:04:04,879 --> 00:04:06,159
(He expanded the empire's borders,)

48
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,280
(rectified the court,)

49
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,599
(and brought Daliang
a century of prosperity.)

50
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,000
(Until his death,)

51
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:14,000
(he clung to a faded strip)

52
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,599
(of red silk.)

53
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,399
(Shiqi,)

54
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:27,279
(keep going.)

55
00:04:27,839 --> 00:04:28,720
(Don't look back.)

56
00:04:30,519 --> 00:04:31,319
(May you)

57
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,720
(find peace and happiness.)

58
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:54,439
Hyah!

59
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:57,639
Hyah!

60
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:02,920
Hyah!

61
00:05:03,260 --> 00:05:04,260
(Imperial power is a poisoned feast.)

62
00:05:04,260 --> 00:05:05,260
(Some are trapped on the throne,)

63
00:05:05,260 --> 00:05:06,260
(aging alone.)

64
00:05:06,260 --> 00:05:07,260
(Some sever all ties and find freedom.)

65
00:05:07,260 --> 00:05:08,260
(Love and hate are but a game.)

66
00:05:08,260 --> 00:05:09,260
(No debts remain in life or death.)

67
00:05:09,260 --> 00:05:10,260
(A fleeting dream, lost to eternity.)

68
00:05:25,940 --> 00:05:27,900
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

69
00:05:28,150 --> 00:05:31,120
ظآزA celestial bird
brushes the mountain's edgeظآز

70
00:05:32,980 --> 00:05:34,460
ظآزWings of light drift through the airظآز

71
00:05:34,460 --> 00:05:38,140
ظآزLike blossoms that refuse to fadeظآز

72
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:41,940
ظآزIt asks no right or wrongظآز

73
00:05:42,180 --> 00:05:44,940
ظآزNor fears the turning of fateظآز

74
00:05:46,060 --> 00:05:47,660
ظآزA trace of spring on the windظآز

75
00:05:47,740 --> 00:05:50,300
ظآزA whisper of a broken heartظآز

76
00:05:52,180 --> 00:05:54,260
ظآزA farewell song unfoldsظآز

77
00:05:54,540 --> 00:05:57,460
ظآزCarrying every sorrow within itظآز

78
00:05:57,860 --> 00:05:59,900
ظآزKarma weaves its endless threadظآز

79
00:06:00,020 --> 00:06:03,860
ظآزAnd I would follow you
without turning backظآز

80
00:06:04,340 --> 00:06:07,340
ظآزLife and death become
nothing sharp or finalظآز

81
00:06:07,660 --> 00:06:10,740
ظآزLove and hate are carried away
on the breezeظآز

82
00:06:11,340 --> 00:06:13,540
ظآزBefore freedom is ever reachedظآز

83
00:06:13,540 --> 00:06:16,580
ظآزOne must first dissolve into tearsظآز

84
00:06:17,180 --> 00:06:20,260
ظآزLove crosses every cycle
